### Health check
GET http://localhost:3000/api/health

### Products - list with pagination
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products?page=1&limit=2

### Products - invalid page (expected 400)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products?page=-1&limit=2

### Products - create (expected 201)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "USB-C Cable",
  "price": 12.99,
  "category": "electronics"
}

### Products - invalid body (expected 400)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "price": "not-a-number"
}

### Orders - list with pagination
GET http://localhost:3000/api/orders?page=1&limit=2

### Orders - invalid limit (expected 400)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/orders?page=1

### Orders - create with status (expected 201)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerName": "Emma Wilson",
  "total": 79.99,
  "status": "paid"
}

### Orders - create without status (expected 201)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerName": "Noah Brown",
  "total": 24.5
}

### Orders - invalid body (expected 400)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerName": "Invalid Order",
  "total": -1
}
